<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Testimonials — Vihaan's Vision</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Vihaan's Vision home">
    <span class="logo-mark">☀️</span>
    <span class="logo-copy">
      <strong>Vihaan's Vision</strong>
      <small>A world where every child smiles</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a><a href="/events/">Events</a><a href="/donate/">Donate</a><a href="/donation-events/">Donation Events</a><a href="/testimonials/" style="color:#2f6f9f">Testimonials</a><a href="/team/">Team</a><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
  </nav>
</header>


<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="kicker">Testimonials</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Kind words from the community.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Notes and acknowledgements from organizations that have received gifts from Vihaan's Vision.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Washington Health Foundation</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Washington Health Foundation acknowledged Vihaan's in-kind donation of over 100 3D printed keychains.
    </p>

    <article class="testimonial-feature">
      <div class="testimonial-letter">
        <span class="badge">Acknowledgement Letter</span>
        <h3>Washington Health Foundation</h3>
        <p class="testimonial-date">July 14, 2026</p>
        <blockquote>
          “We are deeply appreciative of your generosity and your commitment to improving the
          health and well-being of our community.”
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          The foundation shared that the donated keychains were distributed across various hospital
          departments and thanked Vihaan for supporting patient-first care in the community.
        </p>
        <a
          class="btn light"
          href="/washington-health-foundation-testimonial.pdf"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          View Full Letter
        </a>
      </div>

      <a
        class="testimonial-document"
        href="/washington-health-foundation-testimonial.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        aria-label="Open Washington Health Foundation acknowledgement letter PDF"
      >
        <img
          class="testimonial-preview"
          src="/washington-health-foundation-testimonial.png"
          alt="Washington Health Foundation acknowledgement letter for Vihaan's Vision"
        />
      </a>
    </article>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>☀️ One gift, one child, one ray at a time.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
